<i>noun</i>: 연극 [연ː극] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>연극 [연ː극]</dt><br>
<dd>1. play; drama; theater</dd><br>
<dd>배우가 무대 위에서 대본에 따라 관객에게 연기를 보이는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>An act in which an actor or actress acts on a stage according to a script for the audience.</dd><br>
<dd>2. act; pretense; make-believe</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람에게 거짓을 사실인 것처럼 보이게 하기 위한 말이나 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>A remark or act designed to make others believe something fake as real.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>